Class AttributeDispatcher

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.sonar.server.AttributeDispatcher
public class AttributeDispatcher extends Object
An attribute dispatcher is an adapter for SonarObjects. It provides a pair of simple methods to set and get attributes of those objects.
Author:
Douglas Lau
